<h2 id="what-is-barefootjs">What is Barefoot.js</h2>
<p>I really like the look of inline-footnotes created by <a href="https://github.com/lemonmade/bigfoot">Bigfoot.js</a> but it requires <a href="http://jquery.com/">jQuery</a> and loading whole library just to have footnotes seems excessive.</p>
